{
  "stem": "27390.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed-- there were four of them because the father was, the father was dead so there were four of them, and us four-- eight people were staying in that room.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't know what's going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All we had was ersatz coffee, coffee substitute, that's a chicory that we had to eat, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And water-- when, if we needed water, we had to go out to get water from a pump.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was very risky to go out because they could pick up the people as soon as they saw somebody walking.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, we stayed in this room for a couple of days till finally we heard that they surrounded this block.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they're going from room to room to get the people out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was a pit in the room, where they used to keep coal, a coal pit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we all went down into that pit and we covered-- it was covered over with, with the floorboards.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the, we pushed, we managed to push the beds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were two beds in that room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we pushed the beds over the, the, the pit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we heard them come into the room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they went around, and they looked for us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one said to the other-- they saw our rucksacks laying there-- so one said to the other, they must be here somewhere because their rucksacks are here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they looked and looked, but they didn't find us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then they went away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The next day, so, it was a bit quiet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we decided instead of sitting all of us in that room, there were plenty of empty rooms because the people, people were taken away.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
